Title: Head Case
Plot: While discovering an illegal automotive chop shop, the NCIS team stumbles upon a severed head of a Marine, hidden in one of the cars from the shop. When they find possible suspects, the team will have to find the rest of the body and find the murderer.
GuestStars: Chelsea Field, Scott Atkinson, Stephanie Michels, Brian Dietzen, Bruce French, Jamie Martz, Ivar Brogger
